# git-filter-repo mailmap — rewrites author/committer identities before pushing to GitHub.
#
# Format (per line):
#   <new-name> <new-email> <old-name> <old-email>
#   OR
#   <new-name> <new-email> <old-email>
#
# Copy this file to scripts/github-mailmap.txt (gitignored) and keep the template here
# with placeholder values only. One line per identity that needs rewriting.
#
# Example:
metril <1517921+metril@users.noreply.github.com> Real Name <real@email.example>
